## Accessibility, i18n & Openness
When to apply: UI changes, i18n setup, or documentation affecting accessibility/openness.

* Provide accessible UI components (semantic HTML + ARIA where necessary).
* Plan for i18n from start for multi-language projects.
* Respect OSS licenses for third party code and declare license in repo.